{"tid":2239018,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"教育局對教協的看法表示極度遺憾 呼籲教協以免給人「師師相衛」的印象 亦切勿不斷製造恐慌","createTime":"2020-10-11T14:52:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-11T15:31:36.000Z","uid":240362,"like":2,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"ecccebb8872a8c66558f4b9f8b0d8c2fd5180760","tid":2239018,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-11T14:52:38.000Z","msg":"九龍塘宣道小學一名教師，被指於教案中有計劃散播「港獨」信息，遭教育局取消教師註冊，協助該名教師的教協表示，該教師星期一會正式上訴，教協又質疑教育局的裁決欠缺實質證據。<br />\n<br />\n教育局回應指，對教協的看法表示極度遺憾，呼籲教協正確認識香港的憲政地位，以及持守專業精神，維護教育人員的專業操守，包括尊重法律及社會接受的行為準則，以免給人「師師相衛」的印象，亦切勿將個別事件無限放大，不斷製造恐慌。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1554124-20201011.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1554124-20201011.htm&d=aqHBcmSoErOqRK7CI6xlBVCKRJWvDXkpEFRbHtszOvM%3D&h=a5875d80\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1554124-20201011.htm&h=6462cdc4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1554124-20201011.htm</a>"},{"pid":"7c604824da863655bf9310be2075dbaac44ffc54","tid":2239018,"uid":286897,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-11T14:54:02.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"428ebfa1a74ebc3fbd8e67bb645ed63bca8af697","tid":2239018,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7c604824da863655bf9310be2075dbaac44ffc54","tid":2239018,"uid":286897,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-11T14:54:02.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-11T14:54:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b683dd0627c043d295e2912447f80ef5fc8b5e95","tid":2239018,"uid":83251,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy